1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how BettaBase Management (“the App”), developed by ÁlvaroFr, collects, uses, and protects user data.

By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

2. Information We Collect

To use BettaBase Management, users must create an account using an email address and password. We collect the following data:

Account information: email address and hashed authentication data

App usage data: data related to the use of the app features

Purchase status: information about Pro version unlock (in-app purchase status)

We do not collect sensitive personal data such as precise location, contacts, photos, or payment card details.

3. Password Recovery

The App provides a password recovery feature. For this purpose, we may use your registered email address to send recovery instructions.

4. Payments and Pro Features

The App offers optional paid features (“Pro version”) that can be unlocked through Google Play in-app purchases.

All payments are processed securely by Google Play Billing. We do not collect, store, or process payment card or financial information. We only receive purchase confirmation and subscription status from Google to enable Pro features.

5. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data for the following purposes:

Account creation and authentication

Managing Pro feature access

Improving app performance and reliability

Providing customer support when requested

6. Data Sharing and Third-Party Services

The App uses third-party services that may collect information, such as:

Google Play Services
https://policies.google.com/privacy

We do not share your personal data with third parties except when required to provide the service or comply with legal obligations.

7. Data Retention

We retain user data only as long as necessary to provide the app functionality or comply with legal requirements. You may request account deletion at any time.

8. Delete Account

You can request account deletion by following the instructions on our Account Deletion page:
[Delete Account URL]

9. Children’s Privacy

BettaBase Management is not intended for children under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us and we will delete the information promptly.

10. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated “Last updated” date.

11. Contact Us

If you have any questions or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, contact us at:

Email: bettafishapk@gmail.com
